  "slug": "the-opportunity-i-almost-said-no-to-journal",
  "title": "The opportunity I almost said no to",
  "subtitle": "A journal prompt set for examining the hesitation pattern and what it has cost.",
  "excerpt": "A journal prompt set from Day 35 of the MONEY program. Five prompts for tracing what happens between a good opportunity arriving and your answer, and where the delay comes from.",
  "type": "PRACTICE",
  "sourceNotes": "Adapted from Day 35 of MONEY: A 12-Week Tapping Program (Rebecca J Page, 2025).",
  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A journal prompt set from Day 35 of the MONEY program. The delay between a good opportunity arriving and a confident yes is not neutral time: something happens in it. These prompts look at what.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to journalling as a practice? Read ",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "text": "journal prompts as a practice",
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "link",
                "attrs": {
                  "href": "/mindset/journal-prompts-as-practice"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": " first.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "The practice",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Warm-up",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Think of a time a good opportunity arrived and you hesitated. What was the hesitation?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Write the specific opportunity and the specific hesitation. Name that one occasion, not a pattern.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Did you eventually say yes or no? What tipped it?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Write what happened. If you said yes, what shifted? If you said no, what won?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Closer in",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "What did that decision bring, or cost?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Write what followed. Not dramatised, just what actually happened because of the yes or the no.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Is there an opportunity I am hesitating on right now?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Write it specifically. What is the opportunity? What is the hesitation saying?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "What would I do if I trusted that I was ready enough?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Write the action. Not the version where you are perfectly prepared, the version where you are ready enough.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Where this practice comes from",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Adapted from Day 35 of MONEY: A 12-Week Tapping Program (Rebecca J Page, 2025).",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      }
